WEBVTT

00:08.330 --> 00:10.110
Miao Ansu spoke up for you,

00:10.410 --> 00:12.420
saying earlier this year

00:12.440 --> 00:14.519
that sea trade had already peaked

00:14.520 --> 00:17.009
and it was time
to pull Futing's business out.

00:17.010 --> 00:18.020
It‘s like

00:18.970 --> 00:21.009
you knew my uncle would die.

00:21.010 --> 00:21.980
Of course not.

00:22.840 --> 00:24.110
In business,

00:24.930 --> 00:27.070
it's natural to buy low and sell high.

00:28.200 --> 00:30.910
After the big victory at Boat Island,
the trading routes opened up.

00:31.130 --> 00:32.769
Everyone jumped into businesses.

00:32.770 --> 00:34.420
So I had to look for new opportunities.

00:43.720 --> 00:44.630
Dou Zhao,

00:45.400 --> 00:48.780
your heart is racing right now.

00:50.080 --> 00:51.340
I can tell

00:52.610 --> 00:55.310
you're hiding something,
and it has to do with me.

00:56.800 --> 00:58.780
Why won't you tell me?

01:01.440 --> 01:02.340
Tell me!

01:03.570 --> 01:04.460
I...

01:16.050 --> 01:17.260
If I survive through this,

01:17.960 --> 01:19.790
I promise to explain everything.

01:26.010 --> 01:27.460
I will trust you one more time.

01:32.800 --> 01:35.259
I'm Ji Yong, the Secretary
of the Bureau of the Waterways.

01:35.260 --> 01:37.770
The Miao raised funds to build ships
but hasn't repaid the debt.

01:37.770 --> 01:40.180
I was sent by the Futing
Provincial Administration Commission

01:40.190 --> 01:41.870
to interrogate Dou Zhao and Miao Ansu

01:41.960 --> 01:44.510
for the Miao family's shipping case.

03:05.670 --> 03:09.389
=Blossom=
(Adapted from the novel "Blossom" by Zhi Zhi)

03:09.390 --> 03:11.890
=Episode 10=

03:15.720 --> 03:16.710
Young Lady!

03:21.760 --> 03:22.969
He's on our side.

03:22.970 --> 03:24.409
If we're going to act, do it right.

03:24.410 --> 03:25.590
Miss Dou,

03:25.920 --> 03:27.590
you're quite capable.

03:28.160 --> 03:30.740
You've got people everywhere
risking their lives for you.

03:31.040 --> 03:32.780
But too bad, you're in my hands now.

03:33.250 --> 03:35.500
No one can save you now!

03:38.810 --> 03:39.740
That's wrong.

03:39.740 --> 03:41.969
You overstep your authority
and question her in private.

03:41.970 --> 03:44.220
You're the one
who has fallen into my hands.

03:45.110 --> 03:47.879
You, a seven-rank Secretary of
the Ministry of Works are investigating

03:47.880 --> 03:50.409
the Provincial Judicial Office
and Maritime Trade Bureau's case.

03:50.410 --> 03:52.220
Who's really overstepping here?

03:52.220 --> 03:54.960
The Provincial Administration Commission
governs the entire province.

03:54.970 --> 03:56.809
I'm acting under official orders.

03:56.810 --> 03:58.430
By reason and by law, I can be here.

03:58.640 --> 03:59.430
But you?

04:00.130 --> 04:03.180
You're caught red-handed
for coercing confessions.

04:04.160 --> 04:05.620
You think you can stop me

04:06.440 --> 04:08.009
with that?

04:08.010 --> 04:09.500
I haven't even started.

04:09.600 --> 04:10.620
Watch and learn.

04:12.570 --> 04:13.029
Ji Yong!

04:13.030 --> 04:13.569
Official Ji!

04:13.570 --> 04:15.340
Sir, someone's been stabbed.

04:16.160 --> 04:18.230
You attacked a court official.

04:18.640 --> 04:20.380
You'll face charges for this!

04:20.640 --> 04:21.940
Young Lady, watch out!

04:24.170 --> 04:25.060
Come on, make it big.

04:25.810 --> 04:27.489
It would be best if someone died.

04:27.490 --> 04:29.230
I won't be blamed anyway.

04:30.760 --> 04:32.110
Song Mo, stop it!

04:32.110 --> 04:33.900
Young Lady,
be careful not to hurt yourself.

04:33.910 --> 04:34.929
Enough watching. Let's go.

04:34.930 --> 04:35.940
Let her go!

04:37.280 --> 04:38.230
Help me walk.

04:38.280 --> 04:39.110
Yes, sir.

04:43.730 --> 04:45.140
Good thing we prepared

04:45.170 --> 04:46.140
to confuse Ding Wei.

04:46.690 --> 04:48.470
You knew we were putting on a show?

04:48.570 --> 04:51.689
The prison guard told me that Lord Song wanted
to interrogate you himself.

04:51.690 --> 04:53.809
So I'm betting he's smart enough

04:53.810 --> 04:55.940
to see through Ding Wei's setup.

04:57.760 --> 04:59.350
I'm not like you,

04:59.730 --> 05:00.910
who'd die

05:01.050 --> 05:03.230
for beauty wherever you go.

05:11.490 --> 05:13.430
He's still here. Scold me.

05:20.400 --> 05:21.190
Shameless rogue.

05:21.200 --> 05:22.959
What's the problem,
you troublemaker mantis?

05:22.960 --> 05:24.260
Go ahead, kill me if you dare.

05:30.810 --> 05:32.910
Looks like they're doing this for real.

05:35.080 --> 05:36.140
Notify the rest

05:36.250 --> 05:37.500
not to rush in.

05:37.570 --> 05:39.489
Go in when they've had enough.

05:39.490 --> 05:41.180
Yes, sir. I'll notify them.

05:43.440 --> 05:44.439
Kill me if you dare!

05:44.440 --> 05:46.140
- You think I don't dare?
- Kill me, then!

05:47.080 --> 05:48.030
They're gone.

05:48.280 --> 05:49.700
All right. It's over.

05:49.760 --> 05:51.110
They're already gone.

05:52.080 --> 05:53.430
Thank you for your help.

05:53.840 --> 05:54.729
Sulan,

05:54.730 --> 05:56.110
go and check on Su.

05:56.280 --> 05:57.279
Stay alert.

05:57.280 --> 05:59.409
- Let us know if someone's coming.
- Yes, Young Lady.

06:02.930 --> 06:05.140
It will leave a scar
if you don't get it treated soon.

06:06.980 --> 06:08.230
Have you applied the medicine?

06:12.570 --> 06:13.809
The military-grade stuff

06:13.810 --> 06:15.230
only stops the bleeding.

06:15.370 --> 06:17.110
I've got a real remedy here.

06:25.400 --> 06:27.279
People say you're sharp

06:27.280 --> 06:28.580
but cold-hearted.

06:29.930 --> 06:31.009
Seeing

06:31.010 --> 06:33.230
you risked your life
for Fourth Young Lady,

06:33.610 --> 06:35.350
you sure are head over heels for her.

06:37.570 --> 06:39.009
I've known her

06:39.010 --> 06:40.569
since we were kids.

06:40.570 --> 06:41.940
She's my confidante, my soulmate.

06:41.940 --> 06:43.740
She's naturally different
from everyone else.

06:43.750 --> 06:45.700
You wouldn't understand.

06:47.200 --> 06:48.110
Here.

06:51.880 --> 06:53.430
Something feels off.

06:54.010 --> 06:55.870
We shouldn't have let Ji Yong in.

06:56.280 --> 06:58.990
What if he clashes with Deputy Marshal?

07:00.280 --> 07:01.609
The Deputy Marshal told us

07:01.610 --> 07:03.399
to watch Ding Wei closely

07:03.400 --> 07:04.910
and avoid causing trouble.

07:05.050 --> 07:07.140
I'm only worried about Deputy Marshal.

07:07.610 --> 07:09.030
As soon as we arrived in Futing

07:09.030 --> 07:11.209
and found out Fourth Young Lady
was being interrogated,

07:11.209 --> 07:13.700
he couldn't wait but rushed into the prison
to rescue her.

07:14.570 --> 07:15.399
Zheng,

07:15.400 --> 07:17.060
can't you see?

07:17.470 --> 07:19.609
The Deputy Marshal is falling
for Fourth Young Lady.

07:19.610 --> 07:20.430
You...

07:21.130 --> 07:23.110
Do you think he's as foolish as you?

07:26.200 --> 07:27.759
That was interesting.

07:27.760 --> 07:28.820
Sir, this way.

07:38.050 --> 07:39.550
The night Uncle died,

07:39.560 --> 07:41.820
someone saw Ding Wei leaving
his residence late at night.

07:42.690 --> 07:44.810
But that's not solid proof.

07:44.810 --> 07:47.909
However, Ding Wei falsely accusing the Miao
family of colluding with enemies is

07:47.910 --> 07:49.049
just a case of the thief crying thief.

07:49.050 --> 07:50.340
It exposes his own crime instead.

07:50.350 --> 07:51.790
If we can force a confession,

07:51.810 --> 07:53.700
we can take this to the emperor
and convict him.

07:54.810 --> 07:55.569
Ding Wei found

07:55.570 --> 07:57.870
those bandit's blades
on the Miao family's ship.

07:58.010 --> 08:00.270
The Ministry of Imperial Ceremony
is investigating this.

08:00.280 --> 08:02.550
So Ding Wei is rushing
to find a scapegoat.

08:02.730 --> 08:04.060
I've looked into him.

08:04.130 --> 08:06.199
He's been selling
the relief food for money

08:06.200 --> 08:07.820
and exploiting the people.

08:07.960 --> 08:10.380
Now he's anxiously trying
to frame the Miao family.

08:10.570 --> 08:11.729
The deeper we dig,

08:11.730 --> 08:14.030
the more dirty secrets we'll uncover.

08:14.320 --> 08:15.940
If I can board that ship,

08:16.400 --> 08:17.790
I'll find the answers we need.

08:18.610 --> 08:19.300
I have to go.

08:19.310 --> 08:21.460
It's not only about clearing
the Duke of Ding's name,

08:21.470 --> 08:22.530
but also the Miao family's.

08:22.540 --> 08:23.620
I'm going too.

08:26.010 --> 08:26.910
What?

08:27.170 --> 08:29.180
Are you both planning
to board the ship together?

08:35.970 --> 08:36.910
Let's do it this way.

08:37.520 --> 08:39.100
I'll pretend to lick Ding Wei's boot

08:39.280 --> 08:41.670
and steal his official badge
over drinks.

08:52.490 --> 08:55.630
Let's hope Mantis Song
doesn't drag us down.

09:14.490 --> 09:16.270
(The Maritime Trade Bureau Badge)
I've talked to Eunuch Ding.

09:17.830 --> 09:20.009
Since this is about retrieving jewelry
from the ship,

09:20.040 --> 09:22.180
please wait here.

09:23.450 --> 09:24.510
What do you mean?

09:24.800 --> 09:25.940
You dare to stop me?

09:26.160 --> 09:27.490
Please calm down, Your Lordship.

09:27.490 --> 09:29.340
Eunuch Ding explicitly ordered

09:29.400 --> 09:31.550
that no one was to board the ship.

09:36.400 --> 09:37.390
Sir,

09:37.490 --> 09:40.670
it's all clearly written
on this document.

09:41.250 --> 09:43.390
The ship was detained

09:43.760 --> 09:45.369
when I had a shipment

09:45.370 --> 09:47.580
of jewelry from the West.

09:48.490 --> 09:50.060
They're worth a fortune.

09:51.560 --> 09:53.940
If I don't get them back this time,

09:55.400 --> 09:58.550
Madams will never let me off easy.

09:59.760 --> 10:00.700
Comfort me.

10:02.130 --> 10:02.559
There.

10:02.560 --> 10:04.060
It's all right. Don't cry.

10:04.130 --> 10:05.399
My precious little sunshine,

10:05.400 --> 10:06.399
don't cry.

10:06.400 --> 10:07.510
Did you hear that?

10:08.180 --> 10:10.129
We only want to collect
some jewelry on the ship.

10:10.130 --> 10:11.220
Why are you still in my way?

10:11.370 --> 10:12.510
Calm down, Your Lordship.

10:12.800 --> 10:15.310
But the ship is still sealed.

10:15.450 --> 10:17.399
Perhaps I can send some men

10:17.400 --> 10:19.770
to escort the young lady and you
to search for the jewelry.

10:22.850 --> 10:23.940
Sir,

10:24.160 --> 10:27.220
do you take me for a criminal?

10:32.680 --> 10:33.510
Exactly!

10:33.800 --> 10:36.100
With so many people following us,
it's no fun at all.

10:36.250 --> 10:37.759
Can't you be more tactful?

10:37.760 --> 10:38.860
No offense, none at all.

10:39.090 --> 10:41.030
It's just that we can't make that call.

10:44.680 --> 10:45.790
How about now?

10:45.880 --> 10:46.790
Then...

10:47.560 --> 10:48.460
How about this?

10:48.730 --> 10:49.550
I'll only let him

10:49.920 --> 10:52.329
guide you to the cargo hold
to find the jewelry.

10:52.330 --> 10:53.559
One and a half hours

10:53.560 --> 10:54.940
should be enough.

10:55.520 --> 10:56.390
Fine.

10:56.490 --> 10:57.340
Let's go.

11:00.800 --> 11:02.340
What "Young General"?

11:02.400 --> 11:03.980
More like a lovesick fool to me.

11:05.760 --> 11:07.220
Your Lordship, over here.

11:07.880 --> 11:10.220
Are you done
with your little act of charm?

11:10.330 --> 11:11.519
Even real couples

11:11.520 --> 11:13.550
don't cling to each other
every second of the day.

11:13.920 --> 11:15.980
You're usually calm and composed.

11:16.090 --> 11:17.759
But when it comes to acting out

11:17.760 --> 11:19.510
love and romance,

11:19.520 --> 11:21.060
you look like an amateur.

11:21.680 --> 11:24.399
Real married couples
are respectful and polite.

11:24.400 --> 11:26.159
But lovers are different.

11:26.160 --> 11:28.449
They're all always clinging
to each other.

11:28.450 --> 11:31.310
They won't take their eyes
off each other even for a moment.

11:39.550 --> 11:46.050
♪I want to hide like the moon,
like a butterfly drawn to flowers♪

11:46.680 --> 11:47.820
Is this enough?

11:49.010 --> 11:51.980
You're a quick learner.

11:51.990 --> 11:59.410
♪Like ink drops fading into my heart
that turns to longing♪

11:59.870 --> 12:06.290
♪No battle tires me,
for I return to you with every thought♪

12:06.320 --> 12:08.200
Working the night shift
is already hard enough.

12:08.210 --> 12:10.430
Now, you're making
a single guy like me watch this.

12:11.010 --> 12:12.980
At least you two can hug to keep warm.

12:13.090 --> 12:14.060
What about me?

12:20.280 --> 12:21.980
This ship has a draft of five meters.

12:22.330 --> 12:23.980
The route back
to the capital is shallow.

12:24.760 --> 12:25.559
Unbelievable.

12:25.560 --> 12:26.980
This ship will surely run aground.

12:31.280 --> 12:33.100
This ship is so unstable.

12:33.640 --> 12:35.980
It's obvious someone removed
the ballast to destabilize it.

12:36.560 --> 12:38.980
Ding Wei tried to cover it up.
It's solid evidence.

12:40.560 --> 12:41.630
It's not enough.

12:41.760 --> 12:42.679
Not enough?

12:42.680 --> 12:43.670
Your Lordship,

12:43.800 --> 12:45.750
one-quarter of the hour has passed.

12:46.010 --> 12:48.630
Isn't stargazing
and moon-watching enough by now?

12:48.760 --> 12:50.510
You should start looking
for those jewelry.

12:50.760 --> 12:52.550
Lead us to the cargo hold.

12:53.760 --> 12:55.249
Your Lordship, hurry up and find them.

12:55.250 --> 12:56.700
So I can report back.

13:00.730 --> 13:02.060
If someone comes later,

13:02.280 --> 13:04.209
I'll distract them
while you sneak off the ship.

13:04.210 --> 13:05.060
All right.

13:28.970 --> 13:30.750
These fruits are covered in mold.

13:34.880 --> 13:36.510
So is this bronze stove.

13:37.610 --> 13:40.670
Yet the blades we saw that day
only had bloodstains.

13:40.680 --> 13:42.060
There were no signs of corrosion.

13:44.490 --> 13:47.340
It doesn't matter. None of it matters.

13:50.400 --> 13:51.460
Good evening, sir.

13:52.880 --> 13:54.100
Who's up there?

13:54.610 --> 13:55.799
His Lordship and a courtesan.

13:55.800 --> 13:58.000
They went to retrieve
their jewelry in the cargo hold.

13:58.130 --> 13:59.609
Why did you give them the permission?

13:59.610 --> 14:01.670
They had Eunuch Ding's
official document and badge.

14:01.680 --> 14:02.510
Useless fools.

14:03.180 --> 14:04.159
You guys, come with me.

14:04.160 --> 14:05.100
- Yes, sir.
- Yes, sir.

14:07.610 --> 14:09.310
These tea leaves are moldy too.

14:09.450 --> 14:11.860
It proves the bandit's blades
weren't on the ship at all.

14:12.090 --> 14:13.580
They were planted later.

14:15.250 --> 14:17.150
This could all be used as evidence.

14:17.640 --> 14:18.550
Song Mo.

14:27.370 --> 14:28.940
Women can be as capable as men.

14:36.160 --> 14:38.150
In books,
there are beauties like Yan Ruyu.

14:42.800 --> 14:43.750
(It's him.)

14:54.090 --> 14:55.100
Someone's coming.

15:04.370 --> 15:05.310
Prepare yourselves.

15:07.400 --> 15:09.670
Kill anyone who comes out

15:09.880 --> 15:11.050
of that exit.

15:11.060 --> 15:12.009
- Yes, sir!
- Yes, sir!

15:12.010 --> 15:13.390
But that's a Duke's son.

15:15.610 --> 15:18.940
I said kill anyone who comes out.

15:23.610 --> 15:24.399
You there.

15:24.400 --> 15:25.180
Get down there.

16:08.400 --> 16:09.510
They're over there!

16:13.250 --> 16:14.180
Take them down!

16:18.160 --> 16:19.220
Bring the bows!

16:41.800 --> 16:42.630
Jump!

16:56.210 --> 16:56.940
Sir,

16:57.090 --> 16:59.039
Song Mo and a woman boarded the ship

16:59.040 --> 17:00.209
and went straight to the helm.

17:00.210 --> 17:01.910
They were clearly investigating
the case.

17:02.130 --> 17:03.030
Sir,

17:03.040 --> 17:04.630
the blades were planted too hastily.

17:05.080 --> 17:07.140
I'm afraid they'll find something.

17:08.450 --> 17:12.950
Have they found a clue?

17:16.800 --> 17:18.950
(What if I can get Dou Zhao to confess)

17:19.040 --> 17:22.950
(that Miao Ansu
is behind the collusion?)

17:23.210 --> 17:25.060
(Then)

17:25.280 --> 17:27.340
(I'll report it to His Majesty)

17:27.690 --> 17:30.510
(and secure your credit for it.)

17:33.040 --> 17:35.380
Shoot, I fell for his trick.

17:35.520 --> 17:38.190
Also, Eunuch Wang has arrived
at the Provincial Judicial Office.

17:38.250 --> 17:40.230
He's summoned you to report immediately.

17:42.560 --> 17:43.710
You can leave now.

17:43.730 --> 17:44.470
Yes, sir.

17:46.600 --> 17:48.790
I can't. How can I go?

17:48.970 --> 17:49.860
All right.

17:50.120 --> 17:52.519
Hurry home and pack up the valuables.

17:52.520 --> 17:53.860
We need to leave.

17:54.280 --> 17:55.449
Just go and do as I say.

17:55.450 --> 17:56.380
All right.

17:58.840 --> 18:00.190
Oh, no. I'm done for this time.

18:29.360 --> 18:30.900
You're heavily injured.

18:31.040 --> 18:32.230
It is only a scratch.

18:32.970 --> 18:34.270
The arrow didn't go deep.

18:37.360 --> 18:38.710
Let me help you bandage it.

18:39.970 --> 18:40.950
No need.

18:41.560 --> 18:43.030
I've always done it myself.

18:43.280 --> 18:44.620
That won't do.

18:45.250 --> 18:46.420
Just trust me.

18:54.080 --> 18:55.140
Come here.

18:59.120 --> 19:00.750
Are you shy?

19:02.650 --> 19:03.790
Shy? Me? Don't be ridiculous.

19:09.320 --> 19:10.750
Please bear with the pain a little.

19:11.040 --> 19:13.790
If you can't, just scream.

19:17.760 --> 19:18.860
"The Life of Luo Shan."

19:20.320 --> 19:21.380
Miss Dou,

19:22.080 --> 19:23.380
have you watched that play?

19:24.970 --> 19:28.029
- Marvelous!
- Nice!

19:28.030 --> 19:34.770
♪A lone eagle lands on the eaves,
the moonlight shining on the steps♪

19:39.080 --> 19:40.820
(He shielded me from the arrow again.)

19:41.450 --> 19:44.140
(But this time, neither of us died.)

19:47.840 --> 19:48.820
No, I haven't.

19:50.230 --> 19:56.079
♪Does the pain bind us tighter?♪

19:56.080 --> 19:58.750
You didn't come aboard to find evidence.

19:59.080 --> 20:01.370
You must already knew
that Ding Wei falsified everything.

20:01.520 --> 20:03.119
Why did you put up an act with me

20:03.120 --> 20:04.790
instead of arresting him outright?

20:05.120 --> 20:07.060
Someone like Ding Wei

20:07.120 --> 20:09.140
doesn't have the power
to kill Duke of Ding.

20:09.520 --> 20:11.420
Did you notice
the archers on the ship today?

20:11.760 --> 20:12.820
They were highly trained

20:13.080 --> 20:14.620
and far from ordinary soldiers.

20:15.040 --> 20:17.550
The mastermind behind this
must still be hiding.

20:17.840 --> 20:19.660
Ding Wei is just a pawn.

20:20.690 --> 20:22.550
You're using this move to lure them out.

20:23.840 --> 20:26.270
Ding Wei knows of his crimes
and will definitely flee.

20:26.360 --> 20:27.990
We must hurry back now.

20:28.930 --> 20:29.900
Don't worry.

20:30.360 --> 20:32.060
That's what I wanted.

20:35.970 --> 20:37.409
Sir, I packed whatever I could.

20:37.410 --> 20:38.319
No one noticed.

20:38.320 --> 20:39.380
All right.

20:39.760 --> 20:40.510
Sir.

20:41.360 --> 20:42.790
Sir, which direction are we heading?

20:43.280 --> 20:44.359
Any direction.

20:44.360 --> 20:45.230
Just go.

20:49.040 --> 20:50.100
Come on, let's go.

20:53.250 --> 20:54.340
Sir...

20:54.410 --> 20:55.310
Why are we stopping?

20:57.730 --> 20:59.550
Turn around now!

21:00.450 --> 21:01.900
Hurry!

21:13.280 --> 21:14.420
I'm trapped.

21:14.760 --> 21:17.270
Why do they look the same?

21:35.970 --> 21:36.860
Su!

21:40.770 --> 21:42.969
Fourth Young Lady instructed me
to get you out of here

21:42.970 --> 21:44.219
if she didn't return by morning.

21:44.220 --> 21:44.900
Let's go.

21:46.280 --> 21:47.580
Get up slowly.

21:49.970 --> 21:51.079
How dare you

21:51.080 --> 21:52.100
break a prisoner out?

21:59.520 --> 22:00.420
Stop!

22:02.890 --> 22:04.140
Ding Wei falsified evidence

22:04.210 --> 22:05.860
and is now fleeing with stolen goods.

22:05.870 --> 22:08.500
This case will now be handled
by the Northern Pacification Bureau.

22:08.730 --> 22:09.420
But, sir.

22:09.430 --> 22:11.249
This woman has already signed
a confession.

22:11.250 --> 22:12.580
We can't release her.

22:12.970 --> 22:15.140
You're impressively stupid.

22:15.560 --> 22:17.230
If she signed a confession,

22:17.240 --> 22:18.990
there's bound
to be a letter retracting it.

22:19.280 --> 22:20.310
If you don't release her,

22:20.490 --> 22:22.380
are you planning
to share Ding Wei's crimes?

22:24.320 --> 22:25.380
Release her now!

22:29.280 --> 22:30.270
Are you all right?

22:30.320 --> 22:31.420
Let me see.

22:31.760 --> 22:32.860
I'm fine.

22:35.730 --> 22:37.380
Thankfully, your fingers are unharmed.

22:37.840 --> 22:39.060
Zhao,

22:39.760 --> 22:41.340
I didn't betray you.

22:41.490 --> 22:42.510
I know.

22:43.010 --> 22:45.230
The charges against the Miao family
have been cleared.

22:45.240 --> 22:46.900
You don't need
to take the blame anymore.

22:47.600 --> 22:49.660
I'll take you home.

22:50.970 --> 22:51.750
Come.

23:02.450 --> 23:03.860
- Stay where you are!
- Young Lady!

23:05.730 --> 23:07.860
Or I'll end her life with one strike.

23:24.080 --> 23:27.310
The Duke's case is a massive affair.

23:28.120 --> 23:29.380
From the Maritime Trade Bureau

23:29.410 --> 23:32.550
to the Provincial Judicial Office,
and the Grand Coordinator Office yamen.

23:32.650 --> 23:34.470
Who isn't under pressure?

23:34.600 --> 23:37.100
Everyone wants this case closed.

23:37.410 --> 23:38.510
Where are your men now?

23:38.970 --> 23:41.140
They were flaunting
their power here that day.

23:41.930 --> 23:44.900
Why haven't they come to rescue you?

23:44.970 --> 23:46.750
Don't they care about your life?

23:47.280 --> 23:50.929
I was too anxious

23:50.930 --> 23:53.270
and got deceived by their lies!

23:53.280 --> 23:55.599
But the Miao family members
are already in custody.

23:55.600 --> 23:57.230
If they're released now,

23:57.250 --> 23:59.580
how will the authorities face anyone?

23:59.800 --> 24:02.710
Should the people
of Futing revolt or not?

24:06.760 --> 24:07.950
Eunuch Ding,

24:08.210 --> 24:10.620
you're truly a slippery eel
in the officialdom.

24:11.210 --> 24:12.620
Even in a stagnant pond,

24:13.490 --> 24:15.860
you can still find a way
to wriggle out and escape.

24:18.760 --> 24:20.790
But my life is ultimately

24:21.080 --> 24:23.990
in the hands of His Majesty
and Eunuch Wang.

24:25.730 --> 24:27.710
Lord Song, your thirst for revenge

24:28.080 --> 24:29.950
has clouded your judgment.

24:30.490 --> 24:33.380
Eunuch Wang will see to it
that justice is served.

24:36.010 --> 24:37.310
At this point,

24:38.250 --> 24:40.039
continuing your act

24:40.040 --> 24:41.510
is pointless, don't you think?

24:42.930 --> 24:43.860
Tell me.

24:44.490 --> 24:46.900
Who is the mastermind behind all this?

24:49.410 --> 24:51.820
This matter has nothing to do with me!

24:51.890 --> 24:53.790
What mastermind are you talking about?

24:54.490 --> 24:55.950
Have you heard

24:56.760 --> 24:58.790
about my skills using the blade?

24:59.450 --> 25:00.580
General Song,

25:00.930 --> 25:03.190
Duke of Ding is already dead.

25:03.490 --> 25:04.550
Are you really willing

25:04.690 --> 25:05.449
to risk

25:05.450 --> 25:07.990
your career and life for this?

25:08.520 --> 25:10.510
The human body has over
a hundred pressure points

25:10.690 --> 25:12.270
and dozens of joints.

25:12.280 --> 25:13.660
Do you know

25:13.970 --> 25:15.190
which ones hurt the most?

25:17.040 --> 25:18.230
This is just the first cut.

25:19.800 --> 25:20.969
Fine! I'll tell.

25:20.970 --> 25:22.950
I'll tell you.

25:23.210 --> 25:24.900
I'm castrated.

25:25.010 --> 25:27.900
My nephew is the only one left
to carry the bloodline.

25:28.010 --> 25:30.889
A few years ago,
he was foolish to smuggle salt

25:30.890 --> 25:33.409
and was caught by the Duke of Ding.

25:33.410 --> 25:35.900
I begged and pleaded
with the Duke to spare his life.

25:36.320 --> 25:39.550
I was also fine
even if he was exiled as punishment.

25:39.560 --> 25:41.489
But he showed no mercy.

25:41.490 --> 25:43.620
My family line ended because of him.

25:44.490 --> 25:45.420
So

25:46.650 --> 25:48.820
when he was being escorted
to the capital,

25:49.490 --> 25:51.519
I seized the chance for revenge.

25:51.520 --> 25:53.209
Stop trying to fool me

25:53.210 --> 25:54.270
with half-truths.

25:54.490 --> 25:57.550
The Duke's ship was guarded
by skilled Shadow Guards.

25:57.560 --> 25:59.599
How could your useless lackeys

25:59.600 --> 26:00.750
have succeeded?

26:01.080 --> 26:02.230
I'll ask one more time.

26:03.360 --> 26:05.310
Who is the mastermind?

26:05.730 --> 26:07.420
Who lent you the assassins?

26:08.600 --> 26:10.620
It was revenge for ending
my family line.

26:11.010 --> 26:13.510
No one ordered me.

26:13.520 --> 26:16.390
Is it the Chief Military Commission
or the Ministry of Imperial Ceremony?

26:17.210 --> 26:19.100
Even if you say nothing,

26:19.730 --> 26:21.380
as long as your heart is beating,

26:21.450 --> 26:22.449
your muscles are moving,

26:22.450 --> 26:24.060
and your face shows any expression,

26:24.800 --> 26:26.790
I can guess most of it.

26:27.560 --> 26:29.759
You received help from both

26:29.760 --> 26:31.710
but they aren't the masterminds.
Am I right?

26:32.550 --> 26:33.950
Someone from the Grand Secretariat?

26:35.060 --> 26:36.750
Or maybe a member
of the imperial family?

26:40.970 --> 26:42.950
You'd rather sever your tongue
than talk.

26:44.250 --> 26:47.790
Then let's trade your life
for the truth.

27:13.970 --> 27:15.660
Finally, you've shown up.

27:16.010 --> 27:17.270
Drop your bow

27:17.730 --> 27:20.060
or your precious woman
will pay the price

27:20.210 --> 27:22.190
for your recklessness.

27:23.490 --> 27:26.140
They actually believed the act
we've been playing.

27:28.010 --> 27:29.510
I have nothing to do with this case

27:29.690 --> 27:31.790
nor acquainted with him.

27:31.800 --> 27:33.470
You've got the wrong person.

27:34.840 --> 27:36.100
Stop pretending.

27:36.560 --> 27:37.750
Song,

27:38.410 --> 27:40.470
I know she's your woman.

27:40.840 --> 27:44.420
What do you think

27:44.490 --> 27:46.900
about trading her life
for Ding Wei's life?

27:48.170 --> 27:50.420
She's just a pawn to me.

27:50.730 --> 27:52.270
Her death means nothing.

27:52.520 --> 27:53.799
You're lying!

27:53.800 --> 27:55.140
Do you want to bet?

27:56.010 --> 27:58.190
She has a frail little body.

27:58.280 --> 28:01.620
It's as easy to pierce as paper.

28:03.010 --> 28:04.060
Miss Dou,

28:04.520 --> 28:06.190
I'll play a song in memory

28:06.210 --> 28:08.860
of you to show my respect every year

28:09.760 --> 28:11.660
during Qingming Festival.

29:07.080 --> 29:09.570
A forehand strike, then a downward slash
from the upper right.

29:09.600 --> 29:12.270
No wonder the wound is narrow
at the top and wide at the bottom.

29:12.520 --> 29:14.140
It was you who killed Uncle.

29:31.450 --> 29:33.820
Getting involved with Song Yuantang
always means trouble.

29:35.280 --> 29:36.519
Do you think he'd care

29:36.520 --> 29:37.799
about our Young Lady's life

29:37.800 --> 29:39.750
when he risked everything
for the Duke of Ding?

29:41.690 --> 29:42.710
I care.

29:43.280 --> 29:44.380
So I'll go and save her.

29:51.110 --> 29:53.970
(Imperial Edict)

29:56.040 --> 29:58.230
I wanted to use Ding Wei as bait
to lure them out.

29:58.250 --> 30:00.190
I didn't mean for you
to get caught up in this.

30:00.930 --> 30:02.060
I'm sorry.

30:03.450 --> 30:05.790
You helped me
and the Miao family get out of trouble.

30:06.450 --> 30:08.860
Of course,
they think we're on the same side.

30:09.010 --> 30:10.230
This isn't your fault.

30:15.010 --> 30:16.310
Why are your hands shaking?

30:17.760 --> 30:18.820
I'm fine.

30:20.760 --> 30:23.100
Getting aimed by arrows twice
in two days

30:23.320 --> 30:26.310
would scare any average person.

30:27.730 --> 30:28.820
But

30:31.120 --> 30:32.550
you're no average person.

30:38.970 --> 30:40.190
When I was a child,

30:41.280 --> 30:45.140
I had a dream
about being shot by an arrow.

30:46.730 --> 30:47.660
A dream?

31:34.690 --> 31:36.340
Those men are stalling you.

31:36.450 --> 31:38.249
Their real plan
was to set the ship on fire

31:38.250 --> 31:39.510
and silence everyone.

31:41.010 --> 31:43.750
You didn't think I might be waiting
for them to do just that?

32:06.320 --> 32:07.409
Drop your weapons.

32:07.410 --> 32:08.820
Then I'll spare your lives.

32:10.070 --> 32:11.359
You had this planned all along?

32:11.360 --> 32:13.190
It's hard to pry the truth
out of one person.

32:13.200 --> 32:15.620
But much easier with a group.

32:22.490 --> 32:23.620
Next time we meet,

32:23.650 --> 32:25.270
you'll have to tell me about your dream.

32:34.250 --> 32:35.190
Are you all right?

32:52.450 --> 32:55.190
I know you didn't plan
on making it out alive.

32:56.010 --> 32:57.100
But living

32:58.520 --> 33:00.420
beats dying a slow, miserable death.

33:03.930 --> 33:05.550
A thousand cuts

33:05.600 --> 33:08.420
can't match the gratitude
I owe my master.

33:08.970 --> 33:09.900
Fine!

33:11.080 --> 33:13.310
You're all brave, loyal men.

33:14.250 --> 33:17.790
But are your parents,
your wives, and your children

33:18.490 --> 33:20.710
as unyielding as you?

33:21.080 --> 33:22.750
If we can't find your master,

33:23.170 --> 33:24.100
do you think

33:25.320 --> 33:27.900
we can't find your family?

33:29.120 --> 33:31.510
Our Deputy Marshal is fair and just.

33:32.760 --> 33:34.380
The Duke of Ding's death

33:34.490 --> 33:36.990
wasn't your fault
as you were just following orders.

33:37.360 --> 33:38.860
But now that you're captured alive,

33:39.280 --> 33:40.599
think about what your master

33:40.600 --> 33:42.470
will do to your family.

33:42.600 --> 33:43.860
Give up the mastermind,

33:44.450 --> 33:46.750
and I'll protect your loved ones.

33:47.120 --> 33:49.710
A kindness this great,

33:49.840 --> 33:50.990
I, Song Mo,

33:51.890 --> 33:53.190
can afford to offer!

33:53.930 --> 33:55.140
My daughter is only four...

33:55.280 --> 33:56.510
I'll talk.

33:56.650 --> 33:57.420
I'll tell you.

34:00.490 --> 34:01.420
Tell us.

34:12.370 --> 34:13.110
Dou Zhao!

34:14.080 --> 34:15.020
Young Lady!

34:19.810 --> 34:20.369
Eunuch Wang.

34:20.370 --> 34:21.239
Are you hurt?

34:21.240 --> 34:23.710
These men are the assassins
who boarded the ship to kill.

34:24.080 --> 34:25.150
They're about to speak.

34:25.160 --> 34:27.790
After a thorough interrogation
overnight, the truth will come out.

34:29.080 --> 34:31.790
Lord Song,
you're truly brilliant and resourceful.

34:31.840 --> 34:32.900
Thank you for your efforts.

34:33.590 --> 34:35.719
Fourth Young Lady Dou,
I hope you weren't too shaken.

34:35.720 --> 34:36.769
Official Ji,

34:36.770 --> 34:38.860
please send her home first.

34:40.810 --> 34:41.710
Come on.

34:45.720 --> 34:46.719
Your Lordship,

34:46.720 --> 34:50.489
come to the Provincial Judicial Office
for an interrogation

34:50.490 --> 34:54.270
and to officially record your testimony.

34:54.490 --> 34:55.310
Of course.

34:56.370 --> 34:57.070
Lu Ming.

34:57.200 --> 34:57.639
Yes, sir.

34:57.640 --> 34:58.270
Hand them over.

34:59.120 --> 35:00.000
Sheathe your weapons!

35:29.120 --> 35:30.310
Wang Yuan, how dare you!

35:32.290 --> 35:33.380
What are you doing?

35:38.680 --> 35:40.380
It has been determined

35:40.770 --> 35:44.790
that Duke of Ding and his clan
were involved in treasonous actions.

35:45.410 --> 35:47.489
All male members are to be exiled,

35:47.490 --> 35:49.940
and the women returned
to their ancestral home.

35:50.600 --> 35:55.009
Duke of Ding's death
was solely Ding Wei's doing.

35:55.010 --> 35:57.070
This case is now closed.

35:58.720 --> 36:00.020
This is justice?

36:01.010 --> 36:03.230
At least the Jiang family's lives
were spared.

36:04.410 --> 36:06.310
You're here to silence the witnesses.

36:06.850 --> 36:08.790
Song Mo, heir to the Duke of Ying,

36:09.010 --> 36:10.110
obstructed official duties.

36:10.110 --> 36:12.550
You are hereby ordered
to return to the capital immediately.

36:12.560 --> 36:13.710
This is the imperial decree.

36:17.490 --> 36:18.420
You...

36:21.160 --> 36:24.860
Your every word and action
represents His Majesty.

36:25.490 --> 36:28.310
His Majesty knows there's a hidden truth
behind Duke of Ding's death.

36:29.200 --> 36:30.150
Why?

36:31.010 --> 36:33.190
Why did you silence these witnesses?

36:33.640 --> 36:36.110
Why are you covering up the truth?

36:36.330 --> 36:37.270
What kind

36:38.370 --> 36:41.420
of truth is so unbearable to reveal?

36:42.600 --> 36:45.009
I am deeply indebted to His Majesty.

36:45.010 --> 36:48.310
My life was never mine to have.

36:48.410 --> 36:50.150
If you must vent your anger,

36:50.450 --> 36:51.820
you can take my life.

36:52.890 --> 36:56.340
But if you wish to uncover the truth,

36:57.490 --> 36:59.340
not only the Jiang family,

36:59.600 --> 37:01.270
but the Song family,

37:01.330 --> 37:05.270
and even these elites from the Ding Army
who are defying orders,

37:05.720 --> 37:07.380
will all pay the price.

37:17.450 --> 37:20.070
The emperor shared decades
of friendship with Duke of Ding.

37:20.370 --> 37:23.150
Planting seeds of doubt
in His Majesty's heart is nearly impossible.

37:23.520 --> 37:25.289
Who could have commanded

37:25.290 --> 37:27.800
someone like Ding Wei,
a man under the inner palace's control?

37:29.520 --> 37:32.940
Only someone of unparalleled status
could mobilize such forces.

37:33.010 --> 37:34.079
This person

37:34.080 --> 37:36.460
isn't someone we can against.

37:43.850 --> 37:45.310
Tell me why!

37:49.370 --> 37:51.110
There is no why.

37:58.850 --> 38:02.670
From the moment Ding Wei entered
the palace at aged seven

38:04.120 --> 38:08.270
and addressed me as his godfather,

38:08.450 --> 38:11.750
he has attended to me for twenty years.

38:12.890 --> 38:14.900
If there had been any way to save him,

38:15.640 --> 38:18.820
do you think I would have let him die?

38:19.600 --> 38:22.460
Lightning and rain alike
are the emperor's grace.

38:23.120 --> 38:26.710
If the ruler wants his subject to die,
to refuse is disloyalty.

38:27.600 --> 38:28.590
Your Lordship,

38:29.080 --> 38:30.710
I had no choice.

38:31.160 --> 38:32.940
But you still do.

38:46.560 --> 38:47.670
Get up!

38:47.810 --> 38:50.400
Marshal spent his life safeguarding
the nation on the battlefield.

38:50.890 --> 38:53.900
Why should he die in disgrace
and bear such a stain on his name?

39:30.680 --> 39:35.630
(The Ding Army fought to repel enemies
and secure peace for the land.)

39:35.770 --> 39:39.679
(They are the pillars of the court
and the backbone of the nation.)

39:39.680 --> 39:42.119
By imperial decree,
I grant you this pair of twin blades

39:42.120 --> 39:44.630
to honor your great victory.

39:44.630 --> 39:46.079
- This is the imperial decree.
- Your Majesty,

39:46.080 --> 39:48.559
I still prefer using the one

39:48.560 --> 39:49.809
you personally forged for me

39:49.810 --> 39:51.230
before your ascension to the throne.

39:51.490 --> 39:54.110
I fear I might not get used
to these twin blades.

39:55.160 --> 39:56.500
I came to reward the troops.

39:56.600 --> 39:58.159
You reject my gift in front of everyone?

39:58.160 --> 40:00.630
What about my imperial dignity?

40:00.970 --> 40:01.980
You're right.

40:04.600 --> 40:07.190
Then grant them to my successor.

40:07.890 --> 40:08.980
Young Song Mo,

40:11.680 --> 40:12.750
One saber for loyalty.

40:14.160 --> 40:15.150
Take them.

40:16.570 --> 40:17.790
The other, for filial piety.

40:18.010 --> 40:19.409
Please rest assured, Your Majesty.

40:19.410 --> 40:21.079
I will uphold the Ding Army's legacy,

40:21.080 --> 40:22.289
carry on my uncle's mantle,

40:22.290 --> 40:24.630
and serve the court with loyalty
to repay imperial favor!

40:31.890 --> 40:33.110
What loyalty is left

40:34.290 --> 40:35.860
to give?

40:36.890 --> 40:38.070
What country is there

40:39.680 --> 40:41.460
to serve?

40:51.160 --> 40:52.750
What purpose does it serve

40:52.750 --> 40:54.530
to hold the borders
and protect the people?

40:54.930 --> 40:56.460
(A lone young swan)

40:56.680 --> 40:58.150
(beneath a boundless sky.)

40:58.930 --> 41:00.420
(No wonder he only wielded his spear)

41:00.850 --> 41:02.110
(that night)

41:02.720 --> 41:04.380
(instead of the twin blades.)

41:05.040 --> 41:06.590
(So this was the day)

41:07.120 --> 41:08.420
(everything changed.)

41:08.450 --> 41:10.370
(The day he abandoned
loyalty and filial piety)

41:10.970 --> 41:12.230
(after his spirit was crushed,)

41:12.930 --> 41:14.380
(clinging only to vengeance.)

41:20.930 --> 41:22.380
This is an imperial gift.

41:22.640 --> 41:25.750
Damaging it would be a crime
of great disrespect.

41:27.520 --> 41:30.980
An emperor's affection is fleeting.
His justice is a facade.

41:32.410 --> 41:33.980
Why should I remain loyal?

41:35.120 --> 41:36.630
If Heaven wrongs me,

41:37.640 --> 41:38.940
I shall defy Heaven.

41:39.410 --> 41:40.750
If the path betrays me,

41:41.330 --> 41:42.670
I shall renounce the path.

41:43.160 --> 41:45.460
If loyal ministers and valiant generals
can die unjustly,

41:46.120 --> 41:47.750
then why not let me, Song Mo,

41:48.490 --> 41:50.460
become a traitor too?

41:58.550 --> 42:00.470
This is the pass
required to retrieve the boat.

42:00.640 --> 42:01.710
Take it and leave.

42:02.520 --> 42:04.670
I won't drag you into this anymore.

42:06.160 --> 42:07.110
All right.

42:11.850 --> 42:13.710
Then let us never meet again.

42:31.970 --> 42:35.270
My body is poisoned,
and my days are numbered.

42:35.450 --> 42:38.630
(I only regret that before my death,
I failed to clear Duke of Ding's name,)

42:39.290 --> 42:40.860
(and implicated you instead.)

42:42.040 --> 42:45.710
(Staining your honor
and risking your life.)

43:08.210 --> 43:10.009
Do you understand
the true essence of a blade

43:10.010 --> 43:11.440
is not in the killing but in hiding?

43:12.370 --> 43:13.630
From today on,

43:14.040 --> 43:16.500
you are him.

43:17.010 --> 43:20.230
I will pursue the truth to the end
and find the real culprits.

43:20.370 --> 43:23.310
No matter the danger,
it will not stop me!

43:23.950 --> 43:28.429
♪I lean in and gaze at you
as calm as serene waves♪

43:28.430 --> 43:32.190
♪I'm aware of the vast
and turbulent world♪

43:32.350 --> 43:36.740
♪Moving forward alone, the expectations
of many are hard to bear♪

43:36.920 --> 43:40.849
♪When the time comes,
I will cast aside a lifetime of pride♪

43:40.850 --> 43:43.829
♪To wear a flower stick for you♪

43:43.830 --> 43:46.039
♪Or perhaps my heart
yearns for the other side♪

43:46.040 --> 43:48.600
♪Yet there's no place for me
to go in the end♪

43:48.650 --> 43:52.220
♪Your presence
by my side is irreplaceable♪

43:52.280 --> 43:55.800
♪Like a ship crossing
the desolate river♪

43:55.810 --> 43:59.789
♪That brings me
through a chapter of my life♪

43:59.790 --> 44:03.820
♪You are the light
that saves me in the darkness♪

44:04.260 --> 44:07.720
♪Having you is a blessing♪

44:07.880 --> 44:10.060
♪My heart filled with warmth♪

44:10.080 --> 44:13.910
♪By your side,
I spend the rest of my life♪

44:14.240 --> 44:17.380
♪Your presence
by my side is irreplaceable♪

44:17.920 --> 44:21.330
♪Where my heart yearns
is where I will go♪

44:21.770 --> 44:25.310
♪Breaking waves over the desolate river♪

44:25.510 --> 44:29.179
♪The wind rises as my heart finds peace♪

44:29.180 --> 44:33.520
♪You are the light
that saves me in the darkness♪

44:33.580 --> 44:37.309
♪Having you is a blessing♪

44:37.310 --> 44:40.789
♪Only by being by your side♪

44:40.790 --> 44:45.470
♪I can spend the rest of my life♪

44:45.500 --> 44:49.089
♪Until the waves are all spread out♪

44:49.090 --> 44:53.230
♪And the past sinks into the river♪

44:53.300 --> 44:56.590
♪Always together, looking back♪

44:56.900 --> 45:04.200
♪Only sighing at the commotion♪

45:13.790 --> 45:14.749
(No animals were harmed
in the making of this drama)

45:14.750 --> 45:15.789
(Every medical behavior involved
and medicine used in the drama)

45:15.790 --> 45:17.010
(is required by the story.
Please don't try this at home)
